snippet.title: Swift: What are Tuples and Optionals? Algorithms Inside!
snippet.description:
Today we discuss some of the basics of what tuples are and how they're used. More importantly we want to learn why they are useful in some use cases.  As an exercise for this lesson, let's implement a function that finds the two longest names in a list.  Enjoy.
